rows.label: fev07_400_125_msg0001
rows.name:
What are we going to do from
here on out?

rows.label: fev07_400_125_msg0002
rows.name:
There's no point hanging around here...
it's only going to make us feel worse.

rows.label: fev07_400_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Let's head back to Iyasaki and
talk there.

rows.label: fev07_400_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's get going, then. We'll get
somewhere comfortable and then
think about the hard stuff.
